Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.52,0:00:11.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜實在太可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.14,0:00:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想出去工作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.45,0:00:15.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼又在說傻話了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.70,0:00:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次要去的是王都奧斯布里克啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.25,0:00:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要離開拉提娜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.52,0:00:20.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應付那群跟妖魔鬼怪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.84,0:00:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒甚麽分別的臭老頭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.98,0:00:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這樣還有甚麼慰藉可言啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.71,0:00:27.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.01,0:00:33.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.22,0:00:34.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是工作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.85,0:00:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要想著拉提娜在等我回來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.71,0:00:38.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說她好像也交到朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.54,0:00:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不在的期間應該
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.60,0:00:40.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能排解寂寞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.60,0:00:43.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說 我都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.90,0:00:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.97,0:00:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想去就是不想去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.22,0:00:48.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你都知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.65,0:00:49.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就買點拉提娜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.94,0:00:52.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了會開心的手信回來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.24,0:00:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手信
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.62,0:00:54.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.87,0:00:55.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然要去王都
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.80,0:00:58.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買些稀奇的點心回來就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.04,0:01:02.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.28,0:01:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜最喜歡迪爾了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.42,0:01:10.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感覺好像有幹勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.98,0:01:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼眸的深處照映著我的模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.39,0:01:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的笑容令我感到些許耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.64,0:01:41.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在四目相對的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.69,0:01:46.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便已感受到 I feel it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.50,0:01:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如空中出現的\N(那片天空的)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.91,0:01:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那道彩虹一樣\N(彩虹一般)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.25,0:02:02.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃耀著七色光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.79,0:02:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與你共度的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.63,0:02:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使我的內心雀躍不已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.86,0:02:13.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm with you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.85,0:02:16.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論是笑容 又或是傷悲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.35,0:02:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我願分享我的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.02,0:02:23.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你能對我微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.36,0:02:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕猛烈強風 亦或漫長黑夜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.82,0:02:30.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你陪伴在我身邊 僅僅如此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.65,0:02:37.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就令我感覺能再踏出下一步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.45,0:02:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(青年 離家外出)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.71,0:02:55.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不必勉強自己
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.95,0:02:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續睡沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.93,0:03:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 拉提娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.47,0:03:07.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這陣子要讓妳看家了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.39,0:03:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳有辦法努力加油嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.23,0:03:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.86,0:03:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會帶手信回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.16,0:03:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜就拜託你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.16,0:03:28.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可不要太逞強啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.08,0:03:30.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜在等我回來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.83,0:03:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.59,0:03:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪爾 路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.76,0:03:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作的時候要小心喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.05,0:03:45.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在有幹勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.68,0:03:49.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒂蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.64,0:03:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.85,0:03:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要送冒險者到王都去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.11,0:03:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.05,0:03:57.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他似乎是個很難應付的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.32,0:04:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒂蒂 他來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.62,0:04:12.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下奉艾爾迪修提多公爵閣下的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.83,0:04:14.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前來迎接你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.75,0:04:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是迪爾．雷齊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.46,0:04:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.42,0:04:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.84,0:04:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.89,0:04:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 蒂蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.36,0:04:41.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的前任者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.47,0:04:42.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是令對方不開心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.85,0:04:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才被調去邊疆的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.53,0:04:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手信該買些甚麼好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.91,0:04:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不知道女孩子會喜歡些甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.70,0:04:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是買點心比較安全嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.33,0:04:56.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.04,0:04:59.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要想點辦法討他開心才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.55,0:05:02.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.76,0:05:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不嫌棄的話要試試看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.93,0:05:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糖果
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.93,0:05:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.81,0:05:13.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的前任者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.79,0:05:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說就是把對方當成小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.28,0:05:16.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才對方生氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.81,0:05:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能給這種人糖果啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.44,0:05:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.89,0:05:24.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從來沒買糖果給拉提娜吃過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.36,0:05:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她八成會含著糖果鼓起臉頰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.14,0:05:30.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這顏色很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.46,0:05:32.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她應該會很開心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.25,0:05:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.51,0:05:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長途跋涉辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.47,0:05:51.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請 請問
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.18,0:05:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這東西哪裡有賣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.54,0:06:17.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格雷戈爾大人正在等你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.21,0:06:21.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.15,0:06:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了 格雷戈爾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.46,0:06:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以把你那位未婚妻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.93,0:06:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,介紹給我認識嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.55,0:06:29.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 迪爾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.51,0:06:30.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以把你給斬了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.97,0:06:34.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是怒氣沖沖的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.89,0:06:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先 羅潔並不是我的未婚妻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.73,0:06:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.98,0:06:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才剛過來就已經想著要回去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.97,0:06:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想買個能讓小女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.19,0:06:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到會開心的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.64,0:06:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正照你的個性
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.06,0:06:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你除了未婚妻也不會認識其他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.46,0:06:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會喜歡這類東西的年輕女性了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.33,0:06:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 給我站在那不要動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.50,0:07:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少讓我斬你一刀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.38,0:07:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說小女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.30,0:07:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.51,0:07:09.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是個很好的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.66,0:07:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她好可愛好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.32,0:07:13.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且個性又好體貼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.66,0:07:15.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她還揮著她的小手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.20,0:07:17.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我路上要小心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.18,0:07:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在光是回想起來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.63,0:07:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感覺就快哭出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.81,0:07:25.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想快點回去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.99,0:07:27.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.99,0:07:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格雷戈爾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.61,0:07:31.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在馬上出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.45,0:07:32.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.10,0:07:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要立刻殲滅目標
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.30,0:07:34.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以回去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.54,0:07:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.17,0:07:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收養了獨角的魔人族小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.33,0:07:44.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.75,0:07:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然說是魔人族
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.67,0:07:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我跟拉提娜生活
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.84,0:07:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該不會有問題才對
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.26,0:07:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實是沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.30,0:07:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真要說有的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.14,0:07:59.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不時會對那孩子的同族下手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.19,0:08:02.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個事實不會被她知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.56,0:08:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有必要的話凡人族我也會照斬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.15,0:08:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽你這麼說我就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.74,0:08:10.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近發現了疑似是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.94,0:08:12.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"七之魔王"部下的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.99,0:08:15.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是魔族嗎  還是說只是從僕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.91,0:08:17.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前還不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.54,0:08:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你所知
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.00,0:08:22.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔族是透過成為魔王的眷屬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.67,0:08:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藉此獲得遠超乎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.09,0:08:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本身能力之力量的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.88,0:08:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以也未必就是魔人族
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.01,0:08:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說過了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.09,0:08:33.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是工作這些都不重要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.80,0:08:35.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.26,0:08:36.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是老樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.32,0:08:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個亂來的大少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.14,0:08:40.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起生為貴族的地位
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.77,0:08:41.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直以來都是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.93,0:08:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠著這傢伙一路活過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.94,0:08:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的母親是來自異國的繼室
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.32,0:08:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守護家庭就交由兄長們負責
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.86,0:08:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像現在這樣隨心所欲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.89,0:08:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凡事也比較能圓滿解決
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.12,0:08:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你跟著我也比較放心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.54,0:09:00.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.40,0:09:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在父親大人面前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.56,0:09:03.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,態度記得莊重一點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.37,0:09:04.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.38,0:09:09.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之所以將討伐魔王眷屬的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.38,0:09:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交由少數精銳去執行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.01,0:09:14.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為若以國家為主體出動軍隊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.76,0:09:19.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就等同是在向魔王宣戰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.51,0:09:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若要將風險壓在最低限度
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.66,0:09:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並消除魔王的威脅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.77,0:09:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派遣不屬於特定組織的小集團
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.29,0:09:28.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展開奇襲是最有效果的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.15,0:09:31.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待你們的好消息
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.11,0:09:35.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡單說就是叫我們去暗殺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.45,0:09:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是家常便飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.79,0:09:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據斥候的報告
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.58,0:09:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標似乎潛伏於山的另一邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.67,0:09:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要翻山越嶺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.59,0:09:53.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騎飛龍的話一眨眼就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.13,0:09:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪能騎那麼醒目的東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.55,0:09:58.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來要花上好幾天的時間了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.47,0:10:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不夠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.64,0:10:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種程度是在預想之內
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.60,0:10:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且食糧也非常的充裕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.00,0:10:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不夠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.06,0:10:06.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜不夠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.40,0:10:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說甚麼東西不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.36,0:10:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜成分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.32,0:10:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的我缺少拉提娜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.19,0:10:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.56,0:10:20.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.24,0:10:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是出了甚麼問題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.48,0:10:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是牧羊人派
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.02,0:10:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打折賣你 吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.15,0:10:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這家店終於開始
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.55,0:10:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞強迫推銷了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.32,0:10:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且賣相真難看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.40,0:10:45.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為目前正在練習嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.53,0:10:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,練習
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.66,0:10:52.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘做的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.70,0:10:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.83,0:10:55.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是拉提娜的練習作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.83,0:10:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 你放著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.17,0:11:00.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賣出一份了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.88,0:11:02.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.84,0:11:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這妳就自己去問問吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.14,0:11:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等烤得差不多了再跟我說一聲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.44,0:11:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉塔 妳回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.57,0:11:30.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你找到一個不錯的徒弟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.57,0:11:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.35,0:11:32.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為拉提娜她看起來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.93,0:11:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在太寂寞了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.83,0:11:38.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪爾他會平安回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.00,0:11:41.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜妳就放心等吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.04,0:11:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他每次都會對拉提娜說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.71,0:11:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"我回來了"對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.42,0:11:46.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是證據
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.05,0:11:49.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪爾每次都會跟拉提娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.09,0:11:50.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說"我回來了"啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.14,0:11:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.83,0:11:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在拉提娜過來前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.94,0:11:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪爾並不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.60,0:11:55.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.02,0:11:58.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜對那傢伙來說是很特別的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.98,0:12:01.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜 對迪爾很特別
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.71,0:12:02.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.57,0:12:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.68,0:12:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以一直待在迪爾身邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.78,0:12:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳要是不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.22,0:12:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又會像前陣子那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.74,0:12:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬧得不可開交了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.70,0:12:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜出生的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.94,0:12:19.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為拉提娜是壞孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.64,0:12:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以被趕出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.17,0:12:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉古是因為
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.42,0:12:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟拉提娜在一起才死掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.67,0:12:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"拉古"是甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.76,0:12:31.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜男性的親人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.51,0:12:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他陪在拉提娜身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.39,0:12:38.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說拉提娜不是壞孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.26,0:12:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是他的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.44,0:12:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為拉古死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.48,0:12:46.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以拉提娜還是覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.30,0:12:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己是個壞孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.32,0:12:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪爾說拉提娜是好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.82,0:12:55.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明就不是家人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.29,0:12:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但還那樣說拉提娜的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.68,0:12:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪爾是第一個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.70,0:13:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪爾對拉提娜很特別
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.83,0:13:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪爾知道這件事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.09,0:13:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他要是知道拉提娜是壞孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.21,0:13:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜一定會被討厭的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.13,0:13:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜 好怕會被迪爾討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.39,0:13:18.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.48,0:13:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.94,0:13:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在迪爾回來之前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.59,0:13:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要來做個練習
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.86,0:13:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,練習
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.24,0:13:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果妳為他做飯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.76,0:13:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪爾他一定會又驚又喜的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.66,0:13:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜想試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.91,0:13:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯尼斯教教我 拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.04,0:13:48.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她真的是好可愛 我的天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.57,0:13:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊也有一個沒救的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.97,0:13:54.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,監護人跟他的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.97,0:13:57.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們兩人都成了你的徒弟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.10,0:14:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也算不上是甚麼徒弟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.85,0:14:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不過是身為前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.22,0:14:04.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把該教的東西教給他而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.69,0:14:06.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這邊這個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.12,0:14:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是能當作徒弟培育
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.57,0:14:11.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的素質好像也挺不錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.99,0:14:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜 妳的朋友來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.08,0:14:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.09,0:14:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.66,0:14:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.21,0:14:28.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克蘿伊是拉提娜的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.65,0:14:30.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼突然這樣問
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.46,0:14:33.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜對"朋友"不是很了解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.80,0:14:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂的朋友呢 就是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.22,0:14:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該說是同年紀的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.30,0:14:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起玩樂 一起談天的關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.72,0:14:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.35,0:14:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都只有家人跟大人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.38,0:14:47.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.50,0:14:49.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳身邊沒有同年紀的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.07,0:14:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這也沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.15,0:14:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到年紀我想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.65,0:14:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之所以過來找拉提娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.47,0:14:58.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想問妳學校的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.87,0:15:00.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學校
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.12,0:15:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是每年秋天開始的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.20,0:15:04.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會去上課
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.50,0:15:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯迪跟馬賽爾他們也都會去喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.79,0:15:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜年紀和我們一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.36,0:15:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我在想妳會不會去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.75,0:15:12.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜妳今年幾歲了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.76,0:15:17.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七歲 快要八歲了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.30,0:15:18.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.39,0:15:20.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直以為妳才五歲左右呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.10,0:15:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪爾知道這件事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.91,0:15:24.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他沒有問過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.42,0:15:26.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜會去上學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.73,0:15:28.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.36,0:15:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想她一定會去上學的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.65,0:15:33.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.40,0:15:37.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能跟拉提娜一起上學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.84,0:15:38.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好開心喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.82,0:15:41.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克蘿伊很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.70,0:15:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜也很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.33,0:15:44.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人期待
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.54,0:15:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等迪爾回來後
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.33,0:15:49.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要快點準備辦手續了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.92,0:15:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺變得熱起來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.88,0:15:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一帶的地熱溫度很高
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.99,0:15:58.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是充斥著阿夫馬爾神之神威的土地
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.01,0:16:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是龍族繁殖期所偏好的地點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.60,0:16:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是七之魔王手下的龍沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.94,0:16:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.02,0:16:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女人是魔族
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.74,0:16:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(將吾等與神相連的大地啊)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.58,0:16:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(吾以迪爾•雷齊之名下令)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.04,0:16:34.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(依我所願變換樣貌 吞噬一切萬物)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.75,0:16:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,("大地變化")
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.89,0:16:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(大地啊)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.97,0:16:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(以吾之名下令 擊斃吾之仇敵)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.75,0:16:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,("石槍")
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.53,0:16:58.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(保護我們)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.71,0:17:15.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(殺了他 殺了他)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.32,0:17:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.99,0:17:47.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 讓你們久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.03,0:17:49.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要一份牧羊人派
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.58,0:17:50.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.90,0:17:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要一點時間喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.71,0:17:54.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.75,0:17:56.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要等幾個小時都行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.17,0:17:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天就是為了這個來的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.71,0:18:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩份牧羊人派 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.51,0:18:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉塔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.76,0:18:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一會不會是妳端過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.43,0:18:09.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.06,0:18:11.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說想看客人的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.96,0:18:13.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要自己端
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.69,0:18:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你們久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.77,0:18:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為很燙 請小心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.32,0:18:23.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘 妳的手藝進步了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.36,0:18:25.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 艾摩斯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.03,0:18:27.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請慢慢享用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.83,0:18:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然就是要有那個才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.41,0:18:34.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該說是一種療癒感嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.62,0:18:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 趕快開動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.42,0:18:41.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下就擄獲了平時跟小孩無緣的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.17,0:18:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙的心了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.38,0:18:44.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.80,0:18:45.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.80,0:18:48.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳的牧羊人派真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.18,0:18:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.01,0:18:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 吉爾先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.31,0:18:58.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那或許正是那孩子所擁有的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.04,0:19:00.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某種特別的力量呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.94,0:19:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於可以回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.07,0:19:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻去準備回程的飛龍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.60,0:19:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜她現在正在等我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.91,0:19:09.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.95,0:19:12.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出席今天的晚宴也是工作的一環
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.69,0:19:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要 我要回去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.92,0:19:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你不確認一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.49,0:19:22.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫女僕準備好的手信嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.55,0:19:24.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由你親自挑選禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.22,0:19:26.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是才有意義嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.55,0:19:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.30,0:19:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不曉得拉提娜會不會開心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.93,0:19:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 迪爾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.72,0:19:34.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在各方面都已經放棄你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.36,0:19:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.53,0:19:50.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜  拉提娜  拉提娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.70,0:19:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開口第一句就是這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.73,0:19:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼啊 是莉塔嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.10,0:19:56.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.98,0:19:58.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你問拉提娜的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.31,0:19:59.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她正在肯尼斯那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.21,0:20:02.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪爾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.99,0:20:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.21,0:20:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.30,0:20:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了 拉提娜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.97,0:20:12.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留下來看家妳真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.87,0:20:14.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳一定很寂寞吧 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.29,0:20:16.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也覺得很寂寞喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.92,0:20:18.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜覺得很寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.14,0:20:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.88,0:20:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到迪爾平安回來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.42,0:20:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.48,0:20:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.19,0:20:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜果然才是我的慰藉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.24,0:20:32.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有努力過了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.16,0:20:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進一步惡化了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.66,0:20:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.74,0:20:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜 妳的手信
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.52,0:20:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪爾 你等一下喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.75,0:20:44.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半個月的時間太漫長了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.59,0:20:48.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看乾脆將全世界的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.49,0:20:49.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔族驅逐殆盡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.95,0:20:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.20,0:20:54.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就永遠不用跟拉提娜分開了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.47,0:20:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你真的累壞了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.10,0:20:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜她也是非常努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.81,0:21:02.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看她獨自一人待在閣樓的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.61,0:21:04.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本擔心她會不會寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.65,0:21:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我跟她說你回來前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.92,0:21:09.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以來我們的房間睡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.74,0:21:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜想待在迪爾的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.49,0:21:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟迪爾的味道在一起感覺很安心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.87,0:21:16.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.70,0:21:22.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她怎麼 她怎麼會這麼堅強啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.33,0:21:23.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜她不要緊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.65,0:21:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有發生甚麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.46,0:21:28.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她看起來的確是很寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.71,0:21:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但自從有了目標
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.01,0:21:32.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺整個人都振作起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.93,0:21:34.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.37,0:21:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪爾 這是拉提娜做的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.90,0:21:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是拉提娜希望
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.15,0:21:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓迪爾吃努力做的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.78,0:21:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是拉提娜做的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.49,0:21:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努力做的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.66,0:22:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜 拉提娜她
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.12,0:22:03.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親自 為了我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.29,0:22:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃掉太可惜了 我吃不下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.04,0:22:09.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要鬧了 快點吃啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.10,0:22:27.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每過一秒 對妳的喜歡就增加一點
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.94,0:22:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當妳磨蹭我的臉龐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.93,0:22:32.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都變得不再重要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.74,0:22:35.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生在世上的紛爭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.08,0:22:37.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都敵不過這個瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.68,0:22:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以真希望明天或者後天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.58,0:22:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都因為溺愛中毒丟下工作不管
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.50,0:22:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經超乎保護過度 愛操心的毛病
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.32,0:22:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使得我變得異常堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.91,0:22:59.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已下定決心要守護妳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.54,0:23:01.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是為了妳的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.83,0:23:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我甚至能與正義為敵
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.02,0:23:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is 勇者 but 殘念
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.01,0:23:13.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對妳深深著迷
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.76,0:23:16.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜甜蜜蜜或是卿卿我我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.35,0:23:19.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是傻爸爸的末期症狀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.31,0:23:20.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有妳在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.48,0:23:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算當個殘念勇者也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.69,0:23:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以請妳永遠陪伴在我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.36,0:23:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到連冒險也無法繼續的地步
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.11,0:23:36.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is 勇者 but 殘念